                            <comment id="13242736" author="mbertozzi" created="Fri, 30 Mar 2012 21:00:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;quite similar, i get both exception. The FileNotFound of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5665&quot; title=&quot;Repeated split causes HRegionServer failures and breaks table &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-5665&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-5665&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and NotServingRegionException. I&apos;ll retry with 5665 patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
